Author: koicartel
Text: nah i feel u, that kind of stuff has happened to me before where people try to get me to open up and then they don't know how to react so they just kinda meme it off or hit you with a vague "oof that sucks hope ur better soon"  he's your boyfriend and he's meant to be there for you even if he doesn't know what to say, he should be someone you can trust and come to with problems for support and it's shitty that he kinda laughed it off even if he wasn't being serious when he did it
